ORIGINAL WORK

The following components are original works by Ilya Makarov:

  Core Architecture:
  - BBX v6.0 Workflow Format Specification
  - DAG-based Parallel Execution Engine
  - Adapter Registry with Lazy Loading
  - Expression Parser with Safe Interpolation
  - Workspace & State Management System

  Adapters (14 built-in):
  - File Adapter (13 operations)
  - String Adapter (35+ operations)
  - A2A Adapter (Agent-to-Agent Protocol v0.3)
  - Workflow Adapter (nested execution)
  - State Adapter (persistent storage)
  - System/Shell Adapter
  - HTTP Adapter
  - Docker Adapter
  - Python Adapter
  - Logger Adapter
  - Process Adapter
  - Transform Adapter
  - Database Adapter
  - Storage Adapter

  Integrations:
  - MCP Server (40 tools for AI agents)
  - MCP Client (external server integration)
  - Universal Docker Adapter
  - A2A Protocol Implementation
  - BBX Bundler (.bbxpkg format)
  - Secrets Management (Fernet encryption)

